org.swerverobotics.library.interfaces

Interface IThunkDispatcher

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MyFirstOpMode, SyncAutoDriveEncoders, SyncAutoPolygon, SyncAutoPolygonEncoders, SyncAutoServoDemo, SyncColorDemo, SynchAnalogOutputDemo, SynchIMUDemo, SynchLEDDemo, SynchMotorLoopPerf, SynchronousOpMode, SynchServoDemo, SynchSkeletalOp, SynchTelemetryOp, SynchTeleOp, SynchTeleOpModes

    public interface IThunkDispatcher
    Advanced: IThunkDispatcher is an interface through which one can cause work to be thunked to the loop() thread.
    See Also:
    SynchronousOpMode.getThreadThunker(), https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thunk

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void executeOnLoopThread(java.lang.Runnable action)
      Executes the indicated action over on the loop() thread.
      void executeSingletonOnLoopThread(int singletonKey, java.lang.Runnable action)
      Executes the indicated action over on the loop() thread, but replace any pending singleton already there who was queued using the same singleton key.
      int getNewSingletonKey()
      Returns a new singleton key
